name: Non-Alcoholic Sparkling Rosé Can 4-Pack
description: Bursting with delicate fruit flavors of guava, strawberry and kiwi, this refreshing Sparkling Rosé will take you back to your favorite warm weather memories. An easy drinker for a wine newbie or a connoisseur.

name: Non-Alcoholic Brut Can 4-Pack
description: A bold but pleasant Brut wine for any time of day. Not too dry, not too sweet. Hints of lemon, peach and custard keep your tastebuds craving more. Best enjoyed at dinner with Ciara and Russell or at home lounging in Chrissy Teigen’s butter robe

name: Non-Alcoholic Bubbly Red Can 4-Pack
description: A full bodied non-alcoholic red wine for any occasion. Our Non-alcoholic Pinot Noir has smooth velvety tannins with lovely notes of cranberry, plum and blackberry. Well rounded in terms of tannins, fruit and acid ratio. The perfect wine for any crowd.

name: Non-Alcoholic Sauvignon Blanc
description: Surely alcohol-removed Sauvignon Blanc with soft notes of pear, apple and lemon. Crisp, clean and bright. 0.5% ABV white wine.

name: Non-Alcoholic Sparkling Rosé
description: Surely alcohol-removed sparkling rosé has crisp, light notes of strawberry, pear, and tropical fruit balanced with a light acid for a full finish.

name: Non-Alcoholic Sparkling Brut
description: This sparkling non-alcoholic white wine tastes just like the real thing. Perfect for late night drinks and hangover-free mornings.

name: Non-Alcoholic Red Blend
description: A complex, smoky, & layered NA red unlike any other. Dark fruit meets smooth vanilla, rich oak, smoke & spice. Not a varietal. A completely unique sip.
